-------------------------
gnome-disk-utility 2.28.1
-------------------------

gnome-disk-utility provides libraries and applications for dealing
with storage devices.

NOTE NOTE NOTE: This release is API and ABI compatible only with other
                releases in the 2.28.x series.

David Zeuthen (3):
      Bump version to 2.28.1
      Turn some warnings that are not fatal into debug messages
      Update NEWS for release

Matthias Clasen (5):
      Use stock delete and apply buttons
      Fix library translations
      Use translated string for button label
      Translate file system types
      Forgotten string

Tomas Bzatek (2):
      Nautilus extension: ref and unref objects correctly
      Don't crash when presentable has no device

